[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/16/93/169308.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1526496","time":"2019-11-22 21:26","userId":"169308","userName":"ABCDEFG","userSign":"(想遇见外星人)","message":"什么？？讨论不同的理念，不是战争吧","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/44/234440.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1526506","time":"2019-11-22 21:51","userId":"s1366243725","userName":"玖巜iCecream","userSign":"(少女祈祷中。。。。。)","message":"<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">对立统一规律</span><br>唯物辩证法认为，矛盾是事物发展的根本动力，矛盾的同一性和斗争性相结合，推动事物的发展。<br><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">量变质变规律</span><br>量变引起质变，在新质的基础上，事物又开始新的量变，如此交替循环，构成了事物的发展过程。而度这一哲学范畴启示我们，在认识和处理问题时要掌握适度原则。<br><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">否定之否定规律</span><br>否定之否定规律揭示了事物发展的前进性与曲折性的统一，表明了事物的发展不是直线式前进而是螺旋式上升的。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/35/73/357357.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1526509","time":"2019-11-22 21:59","userId":"xduu","userName":"鈴宮華緋 [团长大人]","userSign":"","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"> 课代表"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/77/217781.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1526537","time":"2019-11-22 22:30","userId":"217781","userName":"金刚可怜","userSign":"","message":"不懂"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/56/55670.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1526542","time":"2019-11-22 22:38","userId":"gnwu1996","userName":"Breeze","userSign":"","message":"看到就头疼，给我住嘴 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/97/279798.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1526544","time":"2019-11-22 22:40","userId":"279798","userName":"小白坑HHH","userSign":"","message":"求你别说了T T"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/36/213658.jpg","floor":"#3-5","id":"1526548","time":"2019-11-22 22:56","userId":"213658","userName":"神户猪肉","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">鈴宮華緋 [团长大人]</span> 说:  课代表</q></div>盖老师<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user